<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>eigoPencil - 英語学習を簡単に</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white shadow-md z-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-3 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <a href="/" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600"><span class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600">eigoPencil</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="space-x-4">
                <a href="#features" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600">機能</a>
                <a href="#problem" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600">解決する課題</a>
                <%= link_to login_path, data: { turbo: false }, class: "bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition" do %>
                    無料で始める
                <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="pt-24 pb-16 text-center bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50 to-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">英語学習を、もっと簡単に</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
                覚えたい英単語やフレーズを簡単に管理し、効果的に学習できるプラットフォーム
            </p>
            <!--<%= link_to login_path, data: { turbo: false }, class: "bg-blue-500 text-white text-xl px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition shadow-lg" do %>
                今すぐ無料で始める
            <% end %>-->

          <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
            <div class="relative transform transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <%= image_tag "root_img.png", class: "w-[600px] object-cover rounded-2xl" %>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-white opacity-30"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section id="features" class="py-16 bg-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">eigoPencilの特徴</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏷️</div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">タグ管理</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">単語やフレーズをカテゴリー別に整理</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📇</div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">フラッシュカード</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">繰り返し学習で効果的に記憶</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📊</div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-4">学習進捗</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">正解数と学習状況を可視化</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section id="problem" class="py-16 bg-gray-100">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">こんな悩みありませんか？</h2>
            <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-4">✅</span>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">単語やフレーズをどこにメモしたか忘れてしまう</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-4">✅</span>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">海外ドラマで見かけたかっこいい表現を覚えたいけど管理方法が分からない</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-2xl mr-4">✅</span>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">単語帳作成や復習が面倒で続かない</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-blue-500 text-white text-center">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">すぐに始められる英語学習</h2>
            <p class="text-xl mb-8">まずは無料で、気軽に英語学習を始めましょう</p>
            <%= link_to login_path, data: { turbo: false }, class: "bg-white text-blue-600 text-xl px-10 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition" do %>
                学習を始める
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <p>&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> eigoPencil. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>